column5: Fish that do not show themselves very often. A nice one that my neighbour got off his dock today.
Holy moly! That makes for a good story.
My goodness that is a beast.

Awesome fish!!!!  I bet you your neighbor wasn't too impressed with his catch, lol. I could totally see the "back in the day" stories starting right after he landed it .  And thats totally cool to see an elder with a fish like that, gotta respect that!
What a thick fish. Good for him!!! Doesn't look like a PAB background though.. more like HH !
WOW...how tall is your neighbour...dont tell me....6'3"
Was thinking the same thing.  Nice fish.
WOW!! where were those for us today?!? lol nice catch
Very nice fish. I bet I could listen to that guy talk fishin' all day.
Wow!  Looks like he didn't need any fancy gear either!
That's gets the blood flowing.  Heading out this weekend.  If we get a few half that size, we'll be happy.
